The paper discusses the use of Convolutional Neural Networks (CNN) for generating images based on text descriptions, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also mentions the importance of reading comprehension, which falls under natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of CNNs for text classification and generation also falls under machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Finally, the paper discusses the use of text descriptions as input, which is related to information retrieval (cs.IR).
